{
  "text": "Asked if there's anything we can do to make the instrument more comfortable or improve the contact. I am wrong. All is well. As we have said, this instrument is a weak physically, and continued work times will lengthen this weakness. The continued contact also aids in the continued climb in vital energy of the instrument as well as the integration and vital energy of the group as an unit. The choice is yours. We are pleased. All is well. You are conscientious, continuous. I am Ra. I leave you in the love and in the light of the one infinite creator. Go forth then, my friends, rejoicing in the power and in the peace of the One Infinite Creator Adene.",
